        "eyebrow": "",
        "heading": "<p>Where It All Began.</p>",
        "body_1": "Before the logo. Before the storefront. Before anyone called it a brand, Blessed was already on the court. Outfitting clubs, teams, and players across Europe. From grassroots gyms to the halls of Swiss private schools. The brand didn't create the culture. The culture created the brand.",
        "body_2": "But the more courts we were on, the more we saw the same thing. Kids grinding in gyms nobody was watching. Players chasing dreams most people told them were unrealistic. From Zurich to Chicago, Lausanne to LA, the hunger looked the same everywhere. This wasn't just about jerseys anymore. These people needed more than a uniform. They needed something that represented who they were and what they were working towards.",
